== Lumia专业拍摄 ==

Lumia专业拍摄为Nokia Pro Cam和Nokia Smart Cam合并后的成像应用程式，并在Lumia Black更新中加入。<ref name=PetaPixelNokiaCamera>{{cite news|last=Cade|first=D.L.|title=Nokia Merges Smart and Pro Camera Apps, Brings Raw DNG Support to 1020 and 1520.|url=http://petapixel.com/2013/10/22/nokia-merges-smart-pro-camera-apps-brings-raw-dng-support-1020-1520/|newspaper=PetaPixel|date=22 October 2013|accessdate=2015-05-17|archive-date=2015-09-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150919014013/http://petapixel.com/2013/10/22/nokia-merges-smart-pro-camera-apps-brings-raw-dng-support-1020-1520/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 該程式最初在2013年推出，提供3种基本模式：拍照模式、智慧連拍模式、錄影模式，在智慧連拍模式中，用户使用連續快门，可以在每一帧中的移除特定對象、改变笑脸和创造“段落镜头”。拍照模式有夜景模式和运动模式，錄影模式提供视频录制。诺基亚Lumia 1020和诺基亚Lumia 1520可获取原始DNG。

随着[[Lumia_Cyan|Lumia Cyan]]公佈诺基亚改善诺基亚专业拍摄的低光性能，添加连续自动对焦，添加对动态影像的支持，并提升应用程序的性能。<ref name=ForTheLoveOfTechNokiaCamera>{{cite news|last=Woods|first=R.|title=HOW MUCH DOES LUMIA CYAN IMPROVE THE CAMERA?|url=http://fortheloveoftech.com/2014/08/12/how-much-does-lumia-cyan-improve-the-camera/|newspaper=For the love of Tech|date=12 August 2014|access-date=2015-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160410035255/http://fortheloveoftech.com/2014/08/12/how-much-does-lumia-cyan-improve-the-camera/|archive-date=2016-04-10|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 随着[[Lumia_Denim|Lumia Denim]] 微软更其名为 Lumia 专业拍摄，并推出大量新功能的5.0版本，但仅限于带有PureView 技术的高端设备，同时推出的Nokia Camera Beta 应用更名为''Lumia Camera Classic'' 。<ref name=NokiaPowerUserLumiaCameraClassic>{{cite news|last=None|first=Kamal|title=Lumia 830, 1520, 930 & Icon users can either use Nokia Camera or Lumia Camera classic, until the Lumia Denim update.|url=http://www.nokiapoweruser.com/lumia-830-1520-930-icon-users-can-either-use-nokia-camera-or-lumia-camera-classic-until-the-lumia-denim-update/|newspaper=Nokia PowerUser|date=4 November 2014|accessdate=2015-05-17|archive-date=2017-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170224132415/http://nokiapoweruser.com/lumia-830-1520-930-icon-users-can-either-use-nokia-camera-or-lumia-camera-classic-until-the-lumia-denim-update/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

Lumia专业拍摄5.0拥有一系列新功能，包括更快地拍摄能力、录制每秒 24 且每帧有8.3万像素的4K 视频、自动HDR 和动态闪光灯。由于功能需求所以没有提供给廉价并过时的Lumia 设备。<ref name=LumiaConversationsLumiaCamera>{{cite news|last=Fraser|first=Adam|title=Lumia Camera in focus: capture the moment with quality, ease and speed.|url=http://lumiaconversations.microsoft.com/2014/09/05/lumia-camera-focus-capture-moment-quality-ease-speed/|newspaper=[[Microsoft|Lumia Conversations]]|date=5 September 2014|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150502210808/http://lumiaconversations.microsoft.com/2014/09/05/lumia-camera-focus-capture-moment-quality-ease-speed/|archivedate=2015年5月2日|accessdate=2015年5月17日}}</ref>

== Microsoft照片插件 ==

Microsoft照片插件（舊稱 ''Lumia精彩瞬间''）为Lumia Denim 更新的一个新功能，可以在视频里截取最佳帧并将其存为独立影像， 由于处理能力要求，只有带有较新[[驍龍|高通晓龙]]处理器的[[Nokia_Lumia_ICON|诺基亚 Lumia ICON]] 、诺基亚[[Nokia_Lumia_1520|Lumia 1520]] 、[[Nokia_Lumia_830|诺基亚Lumia 830]] 和 [[Nokia_Lumia_930|诺基亚Lumia 930]] 设备可以运行该集成 Lumia Imaging SDK 的软件。 Lumia 精彩瞬间可以创建两种类型的影像，一种是使用最佳帧可查找图片并将其另存为动态影像，然后在相册或Lumia 影像日志中查看栩栩如生的照片。 另一种是使用连拍模式，可增加闪光效果以显示动作或添加模糊效果以突出运动效果。<ref name=PhoneArenaLumiaMoments>{{cite news|last=F.|first=Alan|title=Lumia Moments now available in the Windows Phone Store.|url=http://www.phonearena.com/news/Lumia-Moments-now-available-in-the-Windows-Phone-Store_id64409|newspaper=Phone Arena|date=5 January 2015|accessdate=2015-05-17|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304035553/http://www.phonearena.com/news/Lumia-Moments-now-available-in-the-Windows-Phone-Store_id64409|dead-url=no}}</ref>

在[[Windows_10行動版|Windows 10行動版]]中微軟決定去除該應用程式的Lumia品牌，在多個Lumia成像應用停止支持的同時。<ref name=OneTechStop-Lumia-Momements-Rebranded-as-Microsoft-Photos-Add-Ins>{{cite news|last=Egwu|first=Izzi|title=Lumia Moments is back in the Windows 10 Mobile Store , rebranded as Photos Add-in app!!|url=http://www.onetechstop.net/2015/09/lumia-moments-is-back-in-the-windows-10-mobile-store-rebranded-as-photos-add-in-app/|newspaper=OneTechStop.net|date=12 September 2015|accessdate=2015-12-16|archive-date=2017-05-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170521201043/http://www.onetechstop.net/2015/09/lumia-moments-is-back-in-the-windows-10-mobile-store-rebranded-as-photos-add-in-app/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== Movie Creator Beta ==

Movie Creator Beta（旧称 ''Nokia Video Director'' 但却仍在[[Windows_Phone_Store|Windows Phone 市集]]上发布）是2014年[[微軟移動|微软移动]]推出的视频制作应用程序。用户可以通过合成照片、视频剪辑、音乐采样并输入文字制作出电影。<ref name=TheNextWebMovieCreatorBeta>{{cite news|last=Woods|first=Ben|title=Meet Microsoft’s new Movie Creator Beta app for Windows Phone.|url=http://thenextweb.com/apps/2014/11/13/meet-microsofts-new-movie-creator-beta-app-windows-phone/|newspaper=The Next Web|date=13 November 2014|accessdate=2015-05-17|archive-date=2019-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191206121638/https://thenextweb.com/apps/2014/11/13/meet-microsofts-new-movie-creator-beta-app-windows-phone/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

在2015年4月Movie Creator Beta 添加对[[Microsoft_OneDrive|Microsoft OneDrive]]和[[4K_resolution|4K]]视频的支持。<ref name=WinBetaMovieCreatorBeta4KvideOneDrive>{{cite news|last=Anderson|first=Kareem|title=Movie Creator for phones becomes more of an Universal App with OneDrive and 4K video support.|url=http://www.winbeta.org/news/movie-creator-phones-becomes-more-universal-app-onedrive-and-4k-video-support|newspaper=WinBeta|date=27 April 2015|accessdate=2015-05-17|archive-date=2015-04-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150428180957/http://www.winbeta.org/news/movie-creator-phones-becomes-more-universal-app-onedrive-and-4k-video-support|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== PhotoBeamer ==

PhotoBeamer（旧称 ''Nokia PhotoBeamer''）是最初由Scalado 开发并被诺基亚收购后一直到Windows Phone 的影像应用程序，可以让用户将联机的Lumia设备上显示的图像，投射到任何联机设备（包括移动电话、平板电脑、笔记版电脑和智能电视）上的PhotoBeamer应用。PhotoBeamer网站会显示一个QR 码，需要用户使用[[Bing_Vision|Bing Vision]]扫描并下载应用程序。<ref name=TechnologPersonalizedNokiaPhotoBeamer>{{cite news|last=Dubey|first=Nimish|title=DailyApp: Nokia PhotoBeamer (Windows Phone) – Lumia Pictures on all Screens!|url=http://techpp.com/2013/01/21/nokia-photobeamer-review/|newspaper=Technology Personalized|date=21 January 2013|accessdate=2015-05-17|archive-date=2017-07-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170730221346/http://techpp.com/2013/01/21/nokia-photobeamer-review/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== Video Upload ==

Video Uploader (旧称 ''Nokia Video Upload'') 是一款YouTube视频上传软件，可以让Lumia用户上传视频到Google旗下的YouTube，最初只支持Lumia 1020，之后扩展到更多设备。<ref name=FierceMobileITNokiaVideoUploader>{{cite news|last=Dano|first=Mike|title=Nokia offers YouTube video uploader app.|url=http://www.fiercemobileit.com/story/nokia-offers-youtube-video-uploader-app/2013-07-25|newspaper=Fierce Mobile IT|date=25 July 2013|accessdate=2015-05-17|archive-date=2016-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307130229/http://www.fiercemobileit.com/story/nokia-offers-youtube-video-uploader-app/2013-07-25|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=PhoneArenaNokiaVideoUploader>{{cite news|last=F.|first=Alan|title=Nokia's YouTube Video Uploader now available for non-GDR2 handsets.|url=http://www.phonearena.com/news/Nokias-YouTube-Video-Uploader-now-available-for-non-GDR2-handsets_id46517|newspaper=Phone Arena|date=17 August 2013|accessdate=2015-05-17|archive-date=2018-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180206131621/https://www.phonearena.com/news/Nokias-YouTube-Video-Uploader-now-available-for-non-GDR2-handsets_id46517|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== Video Tuner ==

Video Tuner（旧称 ''诺基亚Video Tuner''）是一款视频编辑应用程序， 可以进行裁剪、放慢镜头、亮化视频颜色、添加音乐、使用滤镜、旋转、修剪并直接共享至[[Instagram|Instagram]]。 该软件集成了Lumia Imaging SDK使开发者能开发出类似的编辑应用。<ref name=TrustedReviewsVideoTuner>{{cite news|last=Sawh|first=Micheal|title=Video Tuner Windows Phone 8.1 app launches for Nokia smartphones.|url=http://www.trustedreviews.com/news/video-tuner-app-launching-for-nokia-windows-phone-8-1-smartphones|newspaper=Trusted Reviews|date=9 July 2014|accessdate=2015-05-17|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304075718/http://www.trustedreviews.com/news/video-tuner-app-launching-for-nokia-windows-phone-8-1-smartphones|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=WiredCOUKLumiaVideoTuner>{{cite news|last=Collins|first=Katie|title=Video Tuner is a free video-editing app for Lumia owners.|url=http://www.wired.co.uk/news/archive/2014-07/09/nokia-video-tuner|newspaper=Wired|date=9 July 2014|accessdate=2015-05-17|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924011306/http://www.wired.co.uk/news/archive/2014-07/09/nokia-video-tuner|dead-url=no}}</ref>

